Introduction

Giuk, formerly known as CyA, is a member of the band ONEWE under RBW Entertainment. He is the bassist, rapper, and the maknae of the group.

On March 9, 2023, he declared that he would no longer go by the stage name CyA. Instead, he decided to use, Giuk, for all official activities, whether as part of ONEWE or in solo projects.

On April 20, 2023, he debuted as a soloist with the mini album "Psycho Cybernetics: Turn Over".
